ered Yoga School (RYS 200 & RYS 300) with US Yoga Alliance. Our goal is to transform peoples lives through the Ashtanga Vinyasa Yoga system, in order to bring happiness, contentment, peace and fulfillment to all areas of ones own life and then in return, to share these gifts with others. This ancient practice has a place in our modern world, more so now than ever before, and through the experiences of our own truth, our own practice, these teachings have the capacity to bring about enormous transformation and change.\n\nAV108 Yoga School supports each student in their individual practice and recognizes that students are at different levels and for that reason we have specially designed the following courses:\n\nLEVEL 1:  200-Hour Ashtanga Vinyasa Yoga Teacher Training\nLEVEL 2:  300-Hour Ashtanga Vinyasa Yoga Teacher Training\nLEVEL 1+2:  500-Hour Ashtanga Vinyasa Yoga Teacher Training\n\nFor more info visit: \nhttp://ashtangavinyasa108.com/teacher-training-course.html\n\nNamaste", "channel_id": "UCa-2GNiuxBNnPQcav4WI50Q", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa-2GNiuxBNnPQcav4WI50Q", "duration": 219, "view_count": 778, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xntF71z2o-M", "categories": ["Education"], "tags": ["av108yogaschool", "teachertrainingcourse", "yogateachertraining", "ashtangayogateachertraining", "yogateachertrainingmanila", "yogateachertrainingphilippines", "ashtangayoga", "yoga", "yogamanila", "yogaphilippines", "jovannikolic", "ashtangavinyasayoga"], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {}, "subtitles": {}, "comment_count": 2, "like_count": 5, "channel": "AV108 Yoga School", "channel_follower_count": 39, "uploader": "AV108 Yoga School", "uploader_id": "@av108yogaschool3", "uploader_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@av108yogaschool3", "upload_